Future Improvements

Potential future enhancements include:

    Enhanced Security:
        Add liveness detection and anti-spoofing measures to prevent unauthorized access.
        Implement notification systems (e.g., email or SMS alerts) for unrecognized faces.
    Improved User Interface:
        Develop a GUI using PyQt or Tkinter for easier interaction.
        Build a web-based dashboard for real-time monitoring and historical analytics.
    Scalability:
        Extend the system to support multiple cameras and integration with access control systems.
        Improve data storage with a proper database backend.
    Customization & Error Handling:
        Allow on-the-fly registration of new users.
        Enhance error handling and logging for a more robust system.
